hor's opinions\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"not necessarily those\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"CGTN\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On August 8, China celebrates its 16th National Fitness Day.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 660, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 613, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999999158717, \"rank\": 8.410492645362652e-11, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"its 16th National Fitness Day\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, the Paris Summer Olympics are in full swing, and the outstanding performance of Chinese athletes on the field has reignited the passion for national fitness.\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 829, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 752, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999938225414365, \"rank\": 6.143802609664755e-06, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Summer Olympics\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"full swing\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"the outstanding performance\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"the passion\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"national fitness\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the past 20 years, China has made remarkable achievements in developing the national fitness and health sectors.\", \"from\": 831, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999999158717, \"rank\": 8.410492645362652e-11, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the past 20 years\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"remarkable achievements\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 893}, {\"ngram\": \"the national fitness and health sectors\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the State Council first issued the \\\"Outline of the National Fitness Program\\\" in 1995, national fitness has become an integral part of China's national strategy.\", \"from\": 949, \"to\": 1115, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 959, \"end\": 972, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Council_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.315387707310292e-32, \"text\": \"State Council\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Council_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/State_Council_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China\"}, {\"begin\": 1089, \"end\": 1094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999999158717, \"rank\": 8.410492645362652e-11, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Outline\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Fitness Program\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1030}, {\"ngram\": \"national fitness\", \"from\": 1041, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"an integral part\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1085}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Continuous issuance of policy documents, such as the \\\"National Fitness Regulations,\\\" the \\\"Healthy China 2030\\\" blueprint and the \\\"National Fitness Program (2021-2025),\\\" has transformed the national fitness plan from mere sports promotion to a comprehensive health management system, effectively promoting Chinese people's health and well-being.\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1420, \"end\": 1434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999997658051, \"rank\": 1.7876319467560556e-10, \"text\": \"Chinese people\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Continuous issuance\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"policy documents\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1155}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"National Fitness Regulations\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Healthy China 2030\\\" blueprint\", \"from\": 1201, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"National Fitness Program\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"the national fitness plan\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"mere sports promotion\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"a comprehensive health management system\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1396}, {\"ngram\": \"well-being\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The popularization and upgrading of sports facilities have provided a solid material foundation for national fitness.\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The popularization\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"upgrading\", \"from\": 1484, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"sports facilities\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"a solid material foundation\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1556}, {\"ngram\": \"national fitness\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1577}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From cities to rural areas, and from traditional to intelligent sports facilities, the accessibility of sports equipment has continuously improved, and the enthusiasm for public sports activities has been constantly stimulated.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"rural areas\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"intelligent sports facilities\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1660}, {\"ngram\": \"the accessibility\", \"from\": 1662, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"sports equipment\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"the enthusiasm\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"public sports activities\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Huanglong Sports Center in Hangzhou, east China's Zhejiang Province, the introduction of self-service machines, facial recognition devices, and unmanned turnstiles, combined with the \\\"Dynamic Huanglong\\\" applet, has achieved smart venue transformation, enhancing operational efficiency and user experience, and meeting citizens' diverse fitness needs.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1815, \"end\": 1824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huanglong_Scenic_and_Historic_Interest_Area\", \"score\": 0.9999999999749889, \"rank\": 2.5180405008190124e-11, \"text\": \"Huanglong\", \"types\": [\"Q9259\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huanglong_Scenic_and_Historic_Interest_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Huanglong_Scenic_and_Historic_Interest_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 1842, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.679164744899393e-28, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}, {\"begin\": 1852, \"end\": 1862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_China\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"east China\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/East_China\"}, {\"begin\": 1865, \"end\": 1882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhejiang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zhejiang Province\", \"type