.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999938225414365, \"rank\": 6.143802609664755e-06, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"/Xinhua\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2954}, {\"ngram\": \"media publicity\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"education\", \"from\": 2984, \"to\": 2993}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic spirit\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"the stories\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Through media coverage and posts on social platforms, we can stimulate national pride and enthusiasm for sports, further advancing the cause of national fitness.\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3233, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"media coverage\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3094}, {\"ngram\": \"posts\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3104}, {\"ngram\": \"social platforms\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"national pride\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"enthusiasm\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3172}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3183}, {\"ngram\": \"the cause\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"national fitness\", \"from\": 3216, \"to\": 3232}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For instance, in the recently concluded swimming competition, the Chinese men's 4x100m medley relay team broke the 40-year dominance of the American team, winning gold and proving the strength of Chinese swimming, which has sparked public enthusiasm for learning to swim across China.\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3300, \"end\": 3311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people_in_Japan\", \"score\": 0.8869519685521104, \"rank\": 0.11818059187442743, \"text\": \"Chinese men\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people_in_Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_people_in_Japan\"},